				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90oan-Th%E1%BB%A5c/B%E1%BB%87nh-trung-h%E1%BB%89-t%C3%A2n-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-5LCgKX6CD-kW-rjrdzZk5A">Bệnh trung hỉ tân nguyệt - 病中喜新月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90oan-Th%E1%BB%A5c/author-6PN_wShlbQzgayvDwZcw5A">Vương Đoan Thục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-M%E1%BB%99ng-Tu%C3%A2n/B%E1%BB%93ng-Nga-m%E1%BB%99/poem-ov9UlaswQd4yYZb3gBdI9w">Bồng Nga mộ - 蓬莪墓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-M%E1%BB%99ng-Tu%C3%A2n/author-B5Pwn0ab06IhTJvvpJlJ1Q">Nguyễn Mộng Tuân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/C%C3%BAc-m%E1%BB%99ng/poem-RDuYvQZCGOVkecPuRLQEgw">Cúc mộng - 菊夢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/H%C3%A0n-T%C3%ADn/poem-8oTGZyciAVVZOZmlku7-Yw">Hàn Tín - 韓信</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/H%E1%BA%ADu-Nam-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF/poem-PECD5UJe4cpWFXQedwVRsQ">Hậu Nam Đế - 後南帝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-P_O0C8eAMSSE0VWCvRAM-w">Đặng Minh Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/Ki%E1%BB%81u-d%E1%BB%AF-Kim-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-nh%E1%BB%8B-nh%C3%A2n-th%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-bvCH9nf1KU1XHkIEw5sRIQ">Kiều dữ Kim Trọng nhị nhân thệ từ - 翹與金重二人誓詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/Th%E1%BA%ADp-b%E1%BA%A5t-h%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-01/poem-6sev3TH4RlihQnE0qzKaFQ">Thập bất hài kỳ 01 - 十不諧其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-Minh-%C3%A2u/poem-WlcrTsqqVcOiF32NrBuFLA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Minh âu - 水調歌頭－盟鷗</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0/poem-gjczbS0TQgsqTjVlFxPeYw">Trường tương tư - 長相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-8EU5tL9BQ14YEhnmnC8CWA">Trần Đông Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BD-Phi/poem-gRt20uu7GLZRQN2-ZeUSwA">Vịnh Dương Quý Phi - 詠楊貴妃</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-k2nQ5fnr9ZRE2MDraIsNMQ">Nguyễn Tư Giản</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
